{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_8_level_main_08-09_end","storyGroup":"main_8","storySort":19,"storyDependence":"main_8_level_main_08-09_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"M8-6","storyName":"再见，只为再见","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"阿米娅决定让迷迭香留在外面，独自前往面对塔露拉，她命令迷迭香活下去，并帮助其他人活下去。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_08-09_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_08-09","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":17,"next":19,"characters":["盾卫","阿米娅","迷迭香","罗德岛近卫干员？","魏彦吾","陈"]},"lines":[{"type":"header","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"","id":0},{"type":"dialog","id":1},{"type":"character","id":2},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_bg_bg_topout.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":4},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":5},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$nervous_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/act9d0d0/m_avg_nervous_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":6,"musicid":0},{"type":"character","id":7},{"type":"dialog","id":8},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":9},{"type":"delay","time":"1","id":10},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"哈，哈......","id":11,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"罗德岛的医疗技术......是比我们的强......","id":12,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":13},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"向各个感染者聚落派遣医护人员也在我们的计划之内，但是战乱地区的话，让普通医疗干员前去，太危险了。","id":14,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#4","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":15},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"没事，已经......可以了。这样包扎就好了。","id":16,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":17},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"敌人撤退了。战场变大了。我没法再用那个法术，找不到他们。","id":18,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":19},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"那就靠我们的魔族佬吧，他们也很擅长。","id":20,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"感谢你，罗德岛的战士。没有你的骁勇作战，我们的人员伤亡是不可避免的。","id":21,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我刚才听到了，罗德岛的领袖。卡特斯人，你要独自前往指挥塔？","id":22,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":23},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......是，也不是。","id":24,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":25},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"解释一下。","id":26,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":27},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"面对塔露拉的时候，可能只会有我一个。","id":28,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"也许，会有一位来自龙门的战士帮助我......但我假定只有我一个。","id":29,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":30},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你一个人怎么杀死她？你不是大尉。","id":31,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":32},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是，各位也不是。我们人越多，战斗起来就越束手束脚，何况塔露拉比爱国者先生更擅长短时间内压制战场的法术。","id":33,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我要带一支小队进去，只是因为指挥塔内必定也还有其他敌人。","id":34,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":35},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"够吗？","id":36,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我相信我的小队成员。他们都是最可靠也最擅长应对各种状况的战士。如果有我们没法处理的情况，我们会征求你们的帮助。","id":38,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":39},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你想将我们排除在决战之外？","id":40,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":41},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不，我不想主导这次战斗，只不过，先生，游击队有只有你们才能处理的战场。","id":42,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":43},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"你想让我们阻止其他人进入指挥塔。","id":44,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":45},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"没错。","id":46,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#7","focus":"1","id":47},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"......阿米娅，你不想让我去？","id":48,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":49},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"在指挥塔外的战场上你会更安全。","id":50,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":51},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"你不想让我和你一起战斗吗？我们两个人对抗塔露拉......！","id":52,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":53},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"迷迭香，塔露拉的法术饱含能量，你也许很擅长处理各种物理上的伤害方式，但是，火焰的话......","id":54,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":55},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"可我......可她......她杀了Ace，杀了我那么多的亲人！","id":56,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我为什么不能去？","id":57,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":58},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":59,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":60},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我不擅长......我该怎么办？我能怎么办？我以前也有很多事情不擅长的！","id":61,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":62},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你恨塔露拉。","id":63,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":64},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"不然呢，不然呢！我难道不能恨她吗？","id":65,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"迷迭香......","id":67,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"你问的这些我也没有答案。我不能说你不能恨一个你没见过的人......","id":68,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"只是，迷迭香......分别之前，我有一个命令。","id":69,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/e/ed/Avg_char_002_amiya_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":70},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"命令？","id":71,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":72},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"是。","id":73,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":74},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"命令一定要遵守......凯尔希说过，精英干员要做到。我......","id":75,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":76},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯。","id":77,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"——Logos在我们临走前也对我说过，爱国者一生很少把别人称作强敌......","id":78,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"以至于他喜欢用符号、特征和装备称呼别人，反而不太用姓名和种族来代指。","id":79,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是他在刚才，他用菲林来叫你。","id":80,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"也许他认可你了。","id":81,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":82},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"他也这么叫你，他叫你卡特斯。认可什么？认可我这副让人害怕的样子吗？我不想被这么看待。","id":83,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":84},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......但是，如果说许多人把我们当作怪物，那爱国者先生已经被当作怪物很多很多年了。","id":85,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们的身体里都藏着可怕的法术，没错。","id":86,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但他当我们是人。当我们是......人类。","id":87,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":88},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"不是同类吗？都是些......可怕的，一直会被人讨厌的东西。","id":89,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":90},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不。你看看这些游击队战士，这些跟随过其他整合运动领袖的战士，我们的战士......","id":91,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"好的作为会赢得别人尊敬。坏的行为会被别人嫌恶讨厌。","id":92,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们的所作所为才是别人判断我们的途径。就像队员们拥护你，就像盾卫拥护爱国者，就像我们愿意信任凯尔希医生。","id":93,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"迷迭香，我的命令是，你要活下去，也要保证大家能够尽可能地活下去。","id":94,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"为此，哪怕我会死去，你也不能来。","id":95,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":96},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"阿米娅！可你是......我的朋友，我怎么能让......让你一个人！","id":97,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":98},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"不！迷迭香。我保证。","id":99,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我保证我也会活着回来。","id":100,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"所以，不管有人说了什么，不管有人说我遭遇了什么，我们都要各自做主，先完成我们自己的目标。","id":101,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们都要活下去。","id":102,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这个命令，也给在场的所有人。","id":103,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"活下去。","id":104,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"切城营救行动，是为了拯救生命。","id":105,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"核心城潜入行动，也是为了拯救生命。","id":106,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我们不说“为了某种事业我们能抛弃生命”，不。","id":107,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"生命是宝贵的，是重要的，是属于各位自己的。","id":108,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"没有人，没有任何一个人，能够代我们浪费掉这次生命。","id":109,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......没有什么牺牲是必要的。","id":110,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"这种说辞，一定是错的。","id":111,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"Guard！","id":112,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_059","id":113},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"......我在听，阿米娅......罗德岛的领袖。","id":114,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":115},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"对于整合运动也是一样的。","id":116,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":117},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"——","id":118,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"卡特斯！","id":119,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"1","id":120},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯。您说。","id":121,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","name2":"avg_npc_058","focus":"2","id":122},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"这里就交给我们吧。菲林，我们走！去给这只小兔子创造一片理想的战场。","id":123,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":124},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"啊......阿米娅......","id":125,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"2","id":126},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"一定要做。","id":127,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","name2":"char_002_amiya_1","focus":"1","id":128},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":".......","id":129,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"我知道了。我一定会做到。","id":130,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":131},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"嗯，好。","id":132,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/0/09/Avg_char_002_amiya_1.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_002_amiya_1#7","id":133},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"阿米娅小队的成员们，跟我走！","id":134,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"各位，我们活着再见面！","id":135,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ad/Avg_char_002_amiya_7.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_059","id":136},{"type":"dialogue","name":"罗德岛近卫干员？","text":"再见......","id":137,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c5/Avg_avg_npc_059.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":138},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"再见！","id":139,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":140},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":141},{"type":"character","id":142},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/4/46/Avg_bg_bg_topout.png","screenadapt":"coverall","id":143},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":144},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":145},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"那我们，该做我们的事情了。","id":146,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_058","id":147},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"那么，就按游击队这一套来吧。","id":148,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"我们的战场可不在这一小块地方！来吧！让我们把这几条街区，全都变成我们的战区！","id":149,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"盾卫","text":"罗德岛，走！","id":150,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/3/36/Avg_avg_npc_058.png"},{"type":"character","name":"avg_npc_042","id":151},{"type":"dialogue","name":"迷迭香","text":"嗯！","id":152,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6a/Avg_avg_npc_042.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":153},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","initr":"2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":154},{"type":"background","image":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/1/1a/Avg_bg_bg_lungmen_o.png","screenadapt":"coverall","block":"true","id":155},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":156},{"type":"playmusic","intro":"$longmenoffice_intro","key":"https://static.prts.wiki/music/music/beta3_181101/m_bat_longmenoffice_loop.mp3","volume":"0.4","id":157,"musicid":1},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"1","fadetime":"0","id":158},{"type":"blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":159},{"type":"character","name":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","id":160},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"重复一遍，陈警司。","id":161,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":162},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我说的还不够清楚？","id":163,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":164},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"很清楚。清楚到我怀疑自己听错了。","id":165,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"陈警员，这不在你的职权范围之内。","id":166,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"1","id":167},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"法律有国度之分，公理却没有。","id":168,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":169},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"维多利亚皇家近卫学院教了你什么？它有教你脚踏实地，不要好高骛远吗？","id":170,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"1","id":171},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我已经毕业了。我已经是一个为龙门服务的警员了。","id":172,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"那我重复一遍，听好，“我的志愿是加入近卫局，之后，我会加入特别督查组”。","id":173,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"我会捍卫这座城市，也会让它变得更干净。那种事不会再发生了。","id":174,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":175},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"哪种事？","id":176,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"1","id":177},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你是真的忘性很大，还是故意装傻？","id":178,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/6/6b/Avg_char_010_chen_4.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#4","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":179},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"注意你的言辞，陈警员。","id":180,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"1","id":181},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"抱歉，长官。","id":182,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"报告魏长官，我所指的是距今十年前，龙门遭到外部势力侵入，市民遭到绑架并自此失踪的事件。","id":183,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"在我加入近卫局后，我依然会推动龙门对失踪人口的进一步调查和追索。","id":184,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":185},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"陈......你不知道你在说什么。","id":186,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"1","id":187},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"报告长官，我知道。","id":188,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","name2":"char_2005_weiyw_1#5","focus":"2","id":189},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"我不会反对的。那就这样吧，当你做不下去以后，就告诉我。","id":190,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"dialogue","name":"魏彦吾","text":"陈警司，你想在近卫局干几年？","id":191,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/a/ae/Avg_char_2005_weiyw_5.png"},{"type":"character","name":"char_010_chen_1#5","id":192},{"type":"dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......","id":193,"figure":"https://prts.wikihttps://media.prts.wiki/c/c6/Avg_char_010_chen_5.png"},{"type":"dialog","id":194},{"type":"blocker","a":"1","initr":"2","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":195},{"type":"character","fadetime":"0","id":196},{"type":"cameraeffect","effect":"Grayscale","keep":"true","amount":"0","fadetime":"0","id":197},{"type":"text","text":"我没回他。","id":198},{"type":"text","text":"这么多年过来，我一直想的是，我还能干多久？我还要干多久？","id":199},{"type":"text","text":"只是现在我才发现，原来这个答案，一直不是我能决定的。","id":200},{"type":"text","text":"最近赤霄剑在我手里越来越钝。我得到什么时候才会理解，绝影不是逐影而行、绝不放手，而是不再回头？","id":201},{"type":"text","text":"“泪锋之剑，当弃即弃。”","id":202},{"type":"blocker","fadetime":"3","block":"true","id":203},{"type":"image","id":204}],"characters":["盾卫","阿米娅","迷迭香","罗德岛近卫干员？","魏彦吾","陈"]}